        "2206": {
          "vnum": 2206,
          "name": "Fissure",
          "description": "This natural channel must have been caused by a sudden and cataclysmic upheaval of the earth because you see no sign of the smoothing effects of water, and parts of it are pocked and half-melted. It is shaped like a funnel with its narrow end to the south and its wide end to the north. You are very thirsty and should find something to drink.",
