          "vnum": 2207,
          "name": "Cramped Passage",
          "description": "This passage is barely wide enough to allow your shoulders freedom to turn. The crushing space widens to the north, and a heavy slab of rock blocks what looks like a natural chimney that nature has drilled into the solid rock.",
