        "1477": {
          "vnum": 1477,
          "name": "The T-Cross",
          "description": "You are in an area that resounds with the roar of rushing water. To the east you can feel clammy moisture pressing outward. To the south is a narrow and uninviting fissure, while to the west, the canyon travels upward at a very slight angle.",
