        "1349": {
          "vnum": 1349,
          "name": "Edge of the Canyon",
          "description": "The forests break quickly here at the edge of a tremendous canyon, into which pours a thundering sheet of water falling from the very skies above! The water roils within the canyon and fuels a swiftly moving river at its bottom. A narrow, swinging bridge that has seen better days spans the canyon.",
