        },
        "1351": {
          "vnum": 1351,
          "name": "Edge of the Canyon",
          "description": "You stand at the edge of a great, yawning opening in the earth. A roiling curtain of sparkling water roars down into the canyon from the very heavens above, to feed the fabled river of Bruenor's Woe. The river runs southward at the bottom of the canyon into a dark forest far south and west. An old, swinging bridge of rope and leather spans the gap.",
          "grid_x": 2,
          "grid_y": 17,
          "exits": {
            "e": {
              "to_vnum": 111,
              "to_zone": "Flowering Meadows",
              "to_room_name": "Northern Trail",
              "direction": "e",
              "is_cross_zone": true,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "1350": {
          "vnum": 1350,
          "name": "Swinging Bridge",
          "description": "The bridge is old, and was once sturdy, but time has taken its toll on the once seaworthy rope, and the previously sturdy wooden planks. The ropes are covered in the dung of the winged creatures which pause to perch here, high above a river canyon. A fine spray of mist drifts away from a thundering sheet of water which flows down, from the very skies above! The forests of Jharet loom to the west and to the north.",
          "grid_x": 1,
          "grid_y": 17,
          "exits": {
            "e": {
              "to_vnum": 1351,
              "to_zone": "Bruenor's Canyon",
              "to_room_name": "Edge of the Canyon",
              "direction": "e",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "1629": {
          "vnum": 1629,
          "name": "On the River",
          "description": "Your passage along the river is paralleled by a high bank to your west. The bank grows to the stature of a cliff further to the north but tapers down to the same level as the water to the south.",
          "grid_x": 0,
          "grid_y": 33,
          "exits": {
