        "3317": {
          "vnum": 3317,
          "name": "On the River",
          "description": "As you navigate this river bend you cannot help but feel dwarfed by the sheer rock cliff to your west. It rises to a height of 80 feet above your head. This may not seem to be too high, as far as cliffs go, but the way it leans its bulk out over the river is a little daunting.",
